headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Classique Broadway
content:
Are you tired of regulations? Sick of airbags and emission standards and antilock brakes? Whatever happened to just jumping into a beautiful metal box with no seatbelts or safety measures and hoping for the best?

Well good news: the Classique Broadway Muscle Car is here to take you on a first-class cruise around the good ole days. Available now from Legendary Motorsport.
